latestPosts.caption:
BTS that you don’t otherwise get to see. 

Posting a 10 second reel sounds easy but the effort and patience that goes behind a creative project is not talked about enough. The amount of shots, retakes, hours spent editing, lack of motivation and just everyday things that get to you sometimes, all of it. I love creating and am grateful that I get to do it everyday. Keep creating and turning people’s heads♥️🫡
